title: ISENGARD SIEGE DEFENSE - Third Age Total War Gameplay
description:
Third Age Total War Gameplay - Gondor and Dale are on the march to take back the city of Cair Andros.  Isengard and their ally Harad are preparing the defenses.  Both sides are stubborn and willing to do anything for victory!  Enjoy the Battle :D

TheRyanKing will be joining me in today's video!  Be sure to check out his channel - https://www.youtube.com/user/TheBloodyBayonets


If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
